  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR COMMUNITY</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3ce53549c99127bf2d9a9e510dde50a2.poster.avif?t=1675179916\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3ce53549c99127bf2d9a9e510dde50a2.webm?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3ce53549c99127bf2d9a9e510dde50a2.mp4?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Package Dudes</strong> is a great co-op game, where your main task is to sort packages coming on the conveyor belt. Time is ticking, packages never stop coming, so you have to work fast and smart! <br><br>Do whatever it takes to earn valuable points and gain <strong>the title of the employee of the day!</strong> But be careful - There will be floating platforms, lava and other difficulties...<br><br>...Didn't you read the contract carefully?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/8c45e6d8f271e17b631c275809f804dd.poster.avif?t=1675179916\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/8c45e6d8f271e17b631c275809f804dd.webm?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/8c45e6d8f271e17b631c275809f804dd.mp4?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Sort packages!</strong> - Match the number on the package with the number of the drop zone and gain points! Easy, right? Wrong!<br></li><li><strong>Difficult working conditions...</strong> - Wait, did that floor just move? And woah, is this lava real? Sure is, so look out! Maps will only get crazier and crazier, ain’t no rest for the Package Dudes!<br></li><li><strong>Get the employee of the day title!</strong> - All tricks allowed for granting your team valuable points, so throw your package to another dude on your team, and kick away the package of your competition!<br></li><li><strong>Work is better together!</strong> - Share your keyboard even with 3 other players or if you prefer, connect pads and enjoy a game up to 4 players! Simple controls and low entry level makes it a great family game no matter the age!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3d21e70fc018cdfa557345ae3becdc7f.poster.avif?t=1675179916\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3d21e70fc018cdfa557345ae3becdc7f.webm?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3d21e70fc018cdfa557345ae3becdc7f.mp4?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLANNED:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Different types of packages!</strong> - Watch out for packages with special labels: Packages labeled Keep dry must not touch water and if you think about throwing a package labeled Fragile… Make sure it will be caught before hitting the ground!<br></li><li><strong>Team up!</strong> -  Play with your friends in various teams, created however you like! 2v2? 1v3? Sure thing!<br></li><li><strong>Pass the packages to your other team members!</strong> -  Throw them, kick them - foul play your opponents without mercy!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3ce53549c99127bf2d9a9e510dde50a2.poster.avif?t=1675179916\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3ce53549c99127bf2d9a9e510dde50a2.webm?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3ce53549c99127bf2d9a9e510dde50a2.mp4?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Package Dudes</strong> is a great co-op game, where your main task is to sort packages coming on the conveyor belt. Time is ticking, packages never stop coming, so you have to work fast and smart! <br><br>Do whatever it takes to earn valuable points and gain <strong>the title of the employee of the day!</strong> But be careful - There will be floating platforms, lava and other difficulties...<br><br>...Didn't you read the contract carefully?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/8c45e6d8f271e17b631c275809f804dd.poster.avif?t=1675179916\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/8c45e6d8f271e17b631c275809f804dd.webm?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/8c45e6d8f271e17b631c275809f804dd.mp4?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Sort packages!</strong> - Match the number on the package with the number of the drop zone and gain points! Easy, right? Wrong!<br></li><li><strong>Difficult working conditions...</strong> - Wait, did that floor just move? And woah, is this lava real? Sure is, so look out! Maps will only get crazier and crazier, ain’t no rest for the Package Dudes!<br></li><li><strong>Get the employee of the day title!</strong> - All tricks allowed for granting your team valuable points, so throw your package to another dude on your team, and kick away the package of your competition!<br></li><li><strong>Work is better together!</strong> - Share your keyboard even with 3 other players or if you prefer, connect pads and enjoy a game up to 4 players! Simple controls and low entry level makes it a great family game no matter the age!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3d21e70fc018cdfa557345ae3becdc7f.poster.avif?t=1675179916\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3d21e70fc018cdfa557345ae3becdc7f.webm?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228330/extras/3d21e70fc018cdfa557345ae3becdc7f.mp4?t=1675179916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLANNED:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Different types of packages!</strong> - Watch out for packages with special labels: Packages labeled Keep dry must not touch water and if you think about throwing a package labeled Fragile… Make sure it will be caught before hitting the ground!<br></li><li><strong>Team up!</strong> -  Play with your friends in various teams, created however you like! 2v2? 1v3? Sure thing!<br></li><li><strong>Pass the packages to your other team members!</strong> -  Throw them, kick them - foul play your opponents without mercy!</li></ul>",
